# Workshop data

- Train and cross-validate on `data/public.csv` only.
- Evaluate on `data/test/` after fitting on public data (`workshop-evaluate-test`).
- Do not pass `data/test/labels.csv` through pipeline loaders — supply `y` in the env-dict.
